column5: LOL!!!!!!  Reached level 5, 2645 total points, thanks Chris. That's fun.
Thanks Chris...Ive added that to my offline favourites. John.....sheesh man...over 2,000pts. I played just the once and didnt adnace to the next round..had only 198pts. Ill get back at 'er tonight.
WOW....i made it to 1,200 points thats a real fun game...it doesnt take much to entertain my mind either  lol...lol
I made it to 5213 Them darn gators are tuff !!!
I suck, hooked into a fish I just couldn't bring in, kept the line at breaking point and she still kept pulling line until time finally ran out
My score might have been higher if I landed just one of them darned gators, lol.
Got to wait pateintly until the target is directly under  or closer to you and then stick the hooks to him !!!!
gators don't trouble me, its those dang barbels that will spool me/kill my time if you hook em to far from shore

This is a fishing game, I plead the fifth here but first game I scored 12935 and reached level 17 and had 3 poles left. Thank god the gators were so easy to land.  I did have to check out the instructions as i could not get started with my mouse.  ;-)
great - now i'll never get anything done at work! haha cool game
finished at 7957 and level 11 - six poles left on the first try.  I never lost a fish or broke a pole somehow...
